OL,3,CSheffield flats evacuated over fire
OL,4,Csafety concerns
OL,6,FResidents have been told to leave a
OL,7,Fblock of flats in Sheffield over fire
OL,8,Fsafety risks.
OL,10,FRiverside Apartments, on Mowbray
OL,11,FStreet, were evacuated on Wednesday,
OL,12,F15 April, after inspectors served a
OL,13,Fprohibition notice.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for South Yorkshire
OL,16,FFire and Rescue Service said: "The
OL,17,Fnotice prohibits sleeping within the
OL,18,Fresidential flats at any time due to
OL,19,Finadequate means of escape.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776787870
OL,3,CSheffield flats evacuated over fire
OL,4,Csafety concerns
OL,6,F"It will remain in force until the
OL,7,Fmatters are remedied and the notice is
OL,8,Fwithdrawn. Business fire safety
OL,9,Fofficers will continue to work with
OL,10,Fthe business to support them in
OL,11,Fresolving the above issue, and to
OL,12,Fenable the notice to be lifted."
OL,14,FTenants of the block's 10 apartments
OL,15,Fhave been offered #60 a night to find
OL,16,Falternative accommodation.
OL,18,FFranziska Kohlt said she found out at
OL,19,F11pm that she had to leave her flat.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
