FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776787870
OL,3,CSheffield flats evacuated over fire
OL,4,Csafety concerns
OL,6,F"I didn't know what to do," she said.
OL,7,F"There was absolutely nothing in place
OL,8,Ffor us to ` in terms of alternative
OL,9,Faccommodation or anything."
OL,11,FFellow resident Peter Jones added:
OL,12,F"The whole thing's been a shambles. To
OL,13,Fcome back home from work one day and
OL,14,Fthen be kicked out onto the street is
OL,15,Fsomething that I didn't even think
OL,16,Fwould be possible."
OL,18,FAmber Harrison said: "I'm a bit
OL,19,Fconfused by the whole thing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
