PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776787870
OL,3,CSheffield flats evacuated over fire
OL,4,Csafety concerns
OL,6,F"I'd like some clarity on the
OL,7,Fsituation - like to know what's going
OL,8,Fon, when I'll be allowed home, because
OL,9,Fwe don't know and there's not much
OL,10,Fcommunication on that.
OL,12,F"I'd like to feel safe in my home,
OL,13,Freally, and I'd like to be allowed to
OL,14,Fbe here."
OL,16,FIt is unclear when the residents will
OL,17,Fbe allowed to return, but Gareth
OL,18,FFarmer, of property management company
OL,19,FBarnsdales, said residents were being
OL,20,Fkept informed about
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
