OL,3,CSheffield flats evacuated over fire
OL,4,Csafety concerns
OL,6,FHe said: "Immediately, as soon as we
OL,7,Fwere aware of the prohibition notice,
OL,8,Fwe put the wheels in motion to send
OL,9,Fcommunication through to all tenants.
OL,10,FWe did that very effectively. It was
OL,11,Fliterally as we got the news, we
OL,12,Fensured that the tenants were all of
OL,13,Fthe same understanding."
